These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, june, october, february
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, vegafina, baccarat, bluemaster
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, black, aquamarine, orange
City: new-york, colone, paris, nizza
 1. the person who likes black is not to the right of the person who likes brown##8
 2. the person traveling to new-york is not to the left of the person traveling to new-york##8
 3. the person traveling to nizza is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who likes brown is not to the left of the person who likes orange##8
 5. the person traveling to new-york is not to the right of the person traveling to new-york##8
 6. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in january##5
 8. the bluemaster-smoker is between the person traveling to colone and the person who likes black##2
 9. the person traveling to nizza is the baccarat-smoker##1
10. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
11. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the bongani-smoker##3
12. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in june##5
13. the baccarat-smoker is not to the left of the person traveling to nizza##8
14. the person who's birthday is in june is the person traveling to paris##1
15. the person who's birthday is in june is not the person who likes black##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Birthday         | january     | june   | february | october |
| Cigar   | vegafina | bluemaster   | bongani   | baccarat  |
| Color         | black  | aquamarine  | orange  | brown |
| City     | new-york    | paris | colone     | nizza    |

