.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, horror, spy, drama
4 different games are played: backgammon, domino, monopoly, canasta
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, february, june, april
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, subway, bike, bus
 1. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person driving the tram and the person who's birthday is in february##2
 2. the person watching horror movies is not to the right of the person driving the subway##8
 3. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
 4. the person watching scientific movies is not to the right of the person driving the bus##8
 5. the person driving the tram is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##8
 6. the person playing canasta is not to the right of the person watching drama movies##8
 7. the person driving the bike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bus##5
 8. the person driving the bike is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who's birthday is in july is the person driving the subway##1
10. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3
11. the person driving the tram is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##8
12. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
13. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the right of the person playing domino##5
14. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
15. the person watching scientific movies is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
17. the person watching scientific movies is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##8
18. the person playing domino is not to the right of the person driving the subway##8
19. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Movie-Genre      | scientific | spy | drama  | horror  |
| Game          | canasta     | domino | backgammon | monopoly  |
| Birthday   | february    | june  | april | july |
| Transport           | bike | bus | tram    | subway  |

