13. the person playing scrabble is not to the left of the person who's sport is tennis##8
14. the person who's sport is climbing is not to the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##8
15. the person who's sport is climbing is the ranch-style house##1
16. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the right of the modern house##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |     3     |    4    |
| Sport           | cycling | climbing       | tennis      | skateboarding  |
| House   | cottage    | ranch-style | modern   | craftsman   |
| Cigar   | old-henry   | swisher          | alhambra      | aristoff  |
| Game   | domino   | snooker      | chess | scrabble |

